<!--
    FONT SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
    1. Open Android Studio
    2. Right-click res/font → New → Font Resource File
    3. Or download manually from fonts.google.com/specimen/Inter
    4. Place these 3 files in res/font/:
         inter_regular.ttf   (Weight 400)
         inter_semibold.ttf  (Weight 600)
         inter_bold.ttf      (Weight 700)

    Alternatively use Google Fonts in Android Studio:
    Right-click any text view → fontFamily → More Fonts → search "Inter"
-->
